   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Clicking it removes the person from the IWH list (both in the UI and actually)
and adds them as a contributor (and adds a (blank) entry for the project to
their profile). It should also send a "Congratulations! You're now marked as a
contributor for {{project.name}}!" type email to the person.</pre>
